content:
On October 3, the Nanyang Midi Music Festival, which had been prepared for a long time, ended successfully, but was unexpectedly trending on the Internet because of the "zero-yuan purchase" of local villagers.
When the regional jokes are removed, this farce reflects the serious urban-rural divide in China today.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On October 8, the Palestinian armed organization Hamas announced the launch of the "Al-Aqsa Flood" operation against Israel, using artillery and drones to launch attacks and shooting at civilians on the streets.
The video shows that after entering Israel, Hamas looted a large number of women and supplies and transported them back to Gaza.
Subsequently, the Israeli army began to gather and fight back, carrying out air strikes and bombings on the Palestinian area.
At present, this incident has caused a large number of civilian casualties on both sides.
At the same time, Islamic armed organizations in various Middle Eastern countries began to stir.
This century-old feud will usher in a bloodier chapter.
